# Installation
## Requirements
jCoverflip depends upon:
1.     jQuery version 1.3 or later
1.     jQuery UI 1.7.2 (only the core of jQuery UI is required and the themes are not used)

## Installation
1. Install jQuery 1.3+ and jQuery UI 1.7.2
1. Download jCoverflip
1. Add the styles to your site:

        .ui-jcoverflip {
          position: relative;
        }
        
        .ui-jcoverflip--item {
          position: absolute;
          display: block;
        }

1. Include jCoverflip script after jQuery and jQuery UI in the &lt;head&gt; of your HTML document:

        <script type="text/javascript" src="jquery.js"></script>
        <script type="text/javascript" src="jquery.ui.js"></script>
        <script type="text/javascript" src="jquery.jcoverflip.js"></script>
